  I am not doing
  this out of guilt.

15:54.120 --> 15:56.089
 You're looking me in the nose.

15:56.823 --> 15:59.926
 All right, I do feel guilty.

16:00.026 --> 16:04.731
 But, Tina I wish
 you could see this
 from my point of view. I mean,

16:04.764 --> 16:06.599
