16:06.633 --> 16:09.536
  I have to have
  my life organized.

16:09.569 --> 16:13.606
  After all teaching kids,
  saving the whales,
  cleaning the planet

16:13.640 --> 16:16.076
doesn't leave me
very much time.

16:16.109 --> 16:19.112
  -And I'm in the way.
  -I'm sorry.

16:19.145 --> 16:21.748
  But I think we both
  need our own space.

16:23.750 --> 16:25.819
I thought you liked me.

16:25.852 --> 16:27.821
  I thought we were friends.

16:27.854 --> 16:29.856
   I do. And we are.

16:30.690 --> 16:31.891
 Where are you going?

16:31.925 --> 16:34.227
  I'm going to
  find a cheap hovel,

16:34.260 --> 16:37.063
  in a depressed area
  that will have me.

16:48.174 --> 16:51.277
   Mikey and Lisa, that was a
   very well thought-out
   presentation

16:51.311 --> 16:52.679
   on the typewriter.

16:52.712 --> 16:54.314
  -B-plus.
  -All right.

16:54.347 --> 16:56.316
  Stick with me, kid.

16:56.349 --> 17:00.253
  Mikey, I knew you could type
  fast. But I had no idea
  you were that fast.

17:00.286 --> 17:03.857
 ( reading gibberish )

17:03.890 --> 17:05.592
 I think you've misspelled
 ( repeats gibberish )

