   -Who is it?
   -Bran muffin,
   for Carrie Bliss.

20:17.384 --> 20:19.786
 Bran muffin, for Carrie Bliss.

20:22.222 --> 20:24.324
 Tina.

20:24.357 --> 20:27.193
   You are one of my
   favorite people.
   Do you know that?

20:27.227 --> 20:30.096
I am so sorry, Carrie.

20:30.130 --> 20:34.934
  This is your home and I was
  wrong to bring my
  crazy life into it.

20:34.968 --> 20:37.404
But you are who you are,
and that's who I love.

20:37.437 --> 20:40.073
   -That's who you
   can't live with.
   -Come on.

20:40.106 --> 20:43.176
You didn't exactly like
living with me either,
   did you?

20:43.209 --> 20:45.545
   Well, to tell you the truth.
   I didn't.

20:45.578 --> 20:50.050
 With you, everything
 has to be in its place.
 That drove me crazy.

20:50.083 --> 20:54.421
  You got to be so touchy
  over one little
  broken priceless heirloom.

20:54.454 --> 20:55.388
As a matter of fact...

20:55.422 --> 20:58.558
A simple "no" was really
all I was looking for.

21:00.160 --> 21:02.262
   -Friends?
   -Friends.

