   I've rented the guest
   house on the next street.

21:09.903 --> 21:13.106
  It's gonna be great.
  Every morning
  we'll jog together.

21:13.139 --> 21:16.142
 -That's terrific.
 -And we'll have
 our own hot showers.

21:16.176 --> 21:17.844
  -Absolutely.
  -And then,

21:17.877 --> 21:20.480
  I'm gonna make you
  the best breakfast.

21:20.513 --> 21:23.283
   Tina.
   Quit while you are ahead.

